snippet: Cool as their unflappable head coach, Brad Stevens, the Boston Celtics never got down even as their deficit ballooned against the young and athletic Minnesota Timberwolves....
lead_paragraph: Cool as their unflappable head coach, Brad Stevens, the Boston Celtics never got down even as their deficit ballooned against the young and athletic Minnesota Timberwolves.

headline.main: Celtics Rally From 13 Down in 4th to Beat Timberwolves 99-93
